asset.hookText:
Watch the video to find out about the Braun °CoolTec shaver, the world's 1st shaver with active cooling technology, puts skin irritation on ice.

Braun's °CoolTec is a revolutionary new dry shaver that has the power to take the heat out of shaving and puts skin irritation on ice. This power, on top of the stylish design and thoughtful engineering you'd expect from Braun, makes °CoolTec quite possibly the most technologically advanced dry shaver in the world, delivering a simply outstanding shaving performance for men with sensitive skin. 

Find out more at: http://www.braun.com/global/male-grooming/cooltec-shavers.html
